1. Document Purpose

This document catalogs the human-in-the-loop (HITL) interface for the Sovereign Skein and acts as the version-controlled repository for the system's core LLM prompts. By documenting the exact instructions sent to the AI, we ensure reproducible behavior across model updates.

2. Command & Control (C2) - Telegram Menu

The assessor.py node runs a persistent background listener for the following commands via the Telegram Bot API. These commands are the only way the Director interacts with the state machine.

